---

The tools download machine-learning models on first use. Those models carry
their own licenses — all permissive (MIT / Apache-2.0 / BSD-3), never
CC-BY-NC, never gated. Each one shows its license card before downloading and
is listed with it on the Suite's Models page. See specs/00-overview.md for the
model and license policy, and czcore/models.py for the pinned registry.
